summary: Relating to the general municipal election of November 4, 1969 and submitting thereat the proposed Charter Amendments contemplated by Resolutions 22144, 22145, 22146, 22148, 22149, 22150, 22151 & 22152; and requiring the Cit Clerk to certify to the Director of Dept. of Records & Elections of King County as required by law, said proposed amendments in the form of specified ballot titles and said amendments in full, and providing for publication thereof.
